Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在東京租界確認到巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據推測是報告中提到的Freyja彈頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍滯留在神根島是否妥當?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無妨 一切都交給修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般市民當場死亡人數逾千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事後受害者推測將達到2500萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為醫療設施也被完全破壞 無法對市民進行及時救治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京租界已死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是…我…幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這已經不是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再次使用這種兵器 黑騎士團將全軍覆滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 眼下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍降落至東京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 朝比奈遇難 除此之外還有眾多犧牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管這些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍動員搜尋娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個ZERO已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃亡者逃往左側跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 請先重編軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了 逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉婭?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以為逃走的是維蕾塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久違了 毫無節操的電視製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO幹的嗎 皇女殿下成了俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何不再給我多一點信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準腿部 活捉她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是布里塔尼亞的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複 我們是布里塔尼亞的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無戰鬥意願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外交特使?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水無瀨 那台機體是通過正式管道申請的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 親自深入敵人腹地?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂 叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親自去指揮搜救部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 傑雷米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉一定還活著 找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後退至幕張後 重整戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍緊急撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂 我叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要哥哥沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時休戰是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼俾斯麥要撤兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因正在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎沒有交戰意向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 東京也暫時停戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO的指示嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在哥哥身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不也就我們兩人堅持至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在想讓哥哥靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事等一下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 雖然也許沒太大意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥這裡有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會有它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是原本打算給娜娜莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想代替娜娜莉 冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒察覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我痛恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深惡痛絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾次想害死你 不過未能如願而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出去 別再出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來 我仍舊沒意識到 會造成怎樣的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你必須做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拋棄科學保留人心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是捨棄人心來投身科學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德老師也遇到過這種選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就道德敗壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點自知之明還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我製造的Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 ZERO不接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有ZERO也得與修奈澤爾進行會談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我們的頭頭是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先斬後奏是不是有點不妥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屠殺 婦女兒童一個不放過 是ZERO指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈爾特 為什麼沒有馬上抓住修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一架Knightmare護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁這機會為朝比奈報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的專機上裝載有Freyja彈頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引發剛才巨大爆炸的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡爆炸的話 我們和ZERO都難以倖免
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知修奈澤爾打的什麼算盤 但現在只能由我們去會會他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去檢修回歸的紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那交涉由我、千葉、迪特哈爾特 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 找不到扇那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉殿下 您一定要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我在教團中的所見所聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 科奈莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 忙著照顧你們打傷的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城 剛才我也說過請自覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黑騎士團內務清潔副官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做為事務總長扇要的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的一廂情願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 請務必到場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聞是ZERO最元老級的志同道合者 身經百戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去 我曾被你所救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想來道一聲謝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我和你之間的關係還真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運終究讓我們成為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須去找娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倖存者排隊登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓名年齡住所血型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要救治的人去醫務接待台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為避免混亂 請保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 你活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次和ZERO未分勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須先確認會談內容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想他也不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他並不是樂於與人討論的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自背負一切 與他人疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這口吻貌似很熟悉ZERO的為人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你更瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是我和科奈莉婭的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖布里塔尼亞帝國前第11皇子 魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最深愛卻又敬畏的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是布里塔尼亞的皇子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈爾特 你不可能毫無察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該從傑雷米亞和維蕾塔那裡獲得過情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白費心機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想靠這種言論令我們自亂陣腳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們認可ZERO是因為他引發的奇跡而並非家譜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這些奇跡如果有弄虛作假的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄虛作假?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO有特殊能力 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強制對方服從命令的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把它理解成一種強效的催眠術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這力量是奇跡之神?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少說我們家ZERO的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他天資聰穎膽識過人 可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼皇子和GEASS 有證據嗎 證據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證據在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維蕾塔也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真身是布里塔尼亞前皇子魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用GEASS的力量操縱人心的 騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO一直把我們蒙在鼓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 把我們作為棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢 扇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這如果當真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 不能否認ZERO至今為止的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果真有GEASS的話 不是很令人鼓舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將成為對抗布里塔尼亞的強有力武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這份力量只對敵人使用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道對我們也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他操縱自己的親妹妹尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屠殺了前來參加日本特區的11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是正義的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要證據的話就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 你對尤菲使用了GEASS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她屠殺日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次屠殺是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO下令屠殺日本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是偽造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是 被懷疑使用過GEASS的事件與人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁 片瀨少將也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛維斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也深受其害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來高亥的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞投降過來 全都得以說明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也無法保證自己有沒有被他的GEASS操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼想的話 著實可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們曾將Freyja彈頭的事告知過ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為避免無謂的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot上留有通信紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 沒有告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO無法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼的相信他….
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我們對他來說…只是棋子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生 ZERO這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位能否交出我的弟弟ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還有討價還價的餘地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願聞其詳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把日本還來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛自己曾經相信的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要換回日本 不然我無法原諒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 請脫下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手構不著的話 我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 無法觸及之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 能進來嗎 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇希望你去四號倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四號?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體情況我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請脫下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我被抓住的時候 你們都做了些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 這個C.C. …
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你認識的C.C. 已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 不在 娜娜莉也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那魯魯修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉營救來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 我和娜娜莉談了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她幫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候說也許不合適 我的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟吧 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟將我們玩弄於鼓掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經知道你的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說的英雄ZERO 壯志未成身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他勇敢的生前事蹟 將被人們永久傳頌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈爾特 這就是你的劇本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本打算拍完你戰勝布里塔尼亞的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 節目被腰斬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 雖然Knightmare礙事 但扇他們毫無防備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷使用GEASS的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都那麼相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上和吉田也是為你而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 這樣太單方面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧ZERO我們才走到今天不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也聽他一言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和ZERO陪葬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會中了GEASS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說 我是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我願意和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你幹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看來沒機會了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 事到如今才察覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不過是棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一顆特別優秀的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這不過是一盤棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一場遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉鎗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開鎗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂 連蜃氣樓一起解決
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥由我保護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了 蜃氣樓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巴別塔那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亞 ZERO逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mordred能抓住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對守護領域的計算沒想到這麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 我已經沒有活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這動作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大範圍使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 這樣下去你的心臟承受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全員 蜃氣樓被偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有戰鬥單位全力摧毀蜃氣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複 摧毀蜃氣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直被人作為道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…住手 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是教團的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…救我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後又被哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確也許只是被哥哥利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那段時光是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為那段回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於可以 成為人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 別使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 為什麼救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是謊話吧 說什麼想殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞞不過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對哥哥…最瞭解…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的哥哥是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擴大搜索範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請增派地面班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 羅洛 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是結局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 報應才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 正因為如此 謝謝 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救回的這條性命 對我來說還有必須做完的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到 會被迫使用這裡的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸神的黃昏的接續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舊的世界會被毀滅 新的世界將會被創造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾父 查爾斯．D．布里塔尼亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:22:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去地獄的路上 少不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我和你到底是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經知曉了真相  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,追隨我到最後的 竟然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我總是後知後覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是魯路修·Vi·布里塔尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而是魯路修·蘭佩路基的弟弟
